  alignWith-flip []       (y ‚à∑ ys) = refl
  alignWith-flip (x ‚à∑ xs) []       = refl
  alignWith-flip (x ‚à∑ xs) (y ‚à∑ ys) = cong (_ ‚à∑_) (alignWith-flip xs ys)
 
module _ {f : These A A ‚Üí B} where
 
  alignWith-comm : f ‚àò These.swap ‚âó f ‚Üí
                 ‚àÄ xs ys ‚Üí alignWith f xs ys ‚â° alignWith f ys xs
  alignWith-comm f-comm xs ys = begin
    alignWith f xs ys                ‚â°‚ü® alignWith-flip xs ys ‚ü©
    alignWith (f ‚àò These.swap) ys xs ‚â°‚ü® alignWith-cong f-comm ys xs ‚ü©
    alignWith f ys xs                ‚àé

-- align
 
align-map : ‚àÄ (f : A ‚Üí B) (g : C ‚Üí D) ‚Üí
            ‚àÄ xs ys ‚Üí align (map f xs) (map g ys) ‚â°
                      map (These.map f g) (align xs ys)
align-map f g xs ys = begin
  align (map f xs) (map g ys)       ‚â°‚ü® alignWith-map f g xs ys ‚ü©
  alignWith (These.map f g) xs ys   ‚â°‚ü® sym (map-alignWith (These.map f g) xs ys) ‚ü©
  map (These.map f g) (align xs ys) ‚àé
 
align-flip : ‚àÄ (xs : List A) (ys : List B) ‚Üí
             align xs ys ‚â° map These.swap (align ys xs)
align-flip xs ys = begin
  align xs ys                  ‚â°‚ü® alignWith-flip xs ys ‚ü©
  alignWith These.swap ys xs   ‚â°‚ü® sym (map-alignWith These.swap ys xs) ‚ü©
  map These.swap (align ys xs) ‚àé

-- zipWith
 
module _ {f g : A ‚Üí B ‚Üí C} where
 
  zipWith-cong : (‚àÄ a b ‚Üí f a b ‚â° g a b) ‚Üí ‚àÄ as ‚Üí zipWith f as ‚âó zipWith g as
  zipWith-cong f‚âóg []         bs       = refl
  zipWith-cong f‚âóg as@(_ ‚à∑ _) []       = refl
  zipWith-cong f‚âóg (a ‚à∑ as)   (b ‚à∑ bs) =
    cong‚ÇÇ _‚à∑_ (f‚âóg a b) (zipWith-cong f‚âóg as bs)
 
module _ (f : A ‚Üí B ‚Üí C) where
 
  zipWith-zeroÀ° : ‚àÄ xs ‚Üí zipWith f [] xs ‚â° []
  zipWith-zeroÀ° []       = refl
  zipWith-zeroÀ° (x ‚à∑ xs) = refl
 
  zipWith-zero ≥ : ‚àÄ xs ‚Üí zipWith f xs [] ‚â° []
  zipWith-zero ≥ []       = refl
  zipWith-zero ≥ (x ‚à∑ xs) = refl
 
  length-zipWith : ‚àÄ xs ys ‚Üí
                   length (zipWith f xs ys) ‚â° length xs ‚äì length ys
  length-zipWith []       []       = refl
  length-zipWith []       (y ‚à∑ ys) = refl
  length-zipWith (x ‚à∑ xs) []       = refl
  length-zipWith (x ‚à∑ xs) (y ‚à∑ ys) = cong suc (length-zipWith xs ys)
 
  zipWith-map : ‚àÄ (g : D ‚Üí A) (h : E ‚Üí B) ‚Üí
                ‚àÄ xs ys ‚Üí zipWith f (map g xs) (map h ys) ‚â°
                          zipWith (Œª x y ‚Üí f (g x) (h y)) xs ys
  zipWith-map g h []       []       = refl
  zipWith-map g h []       (y ‚à∑ ys) = refl
  zipWith-map g h (x ‚à∑ xs) []       = refl
  zipWith-map g h (x ‚à∑ xs) (y ‚à∑ ys) =
    cong‚ÇÇ _‚à∑_ refl (zipWith-map g h xs ys)
 
  map-zipWith : ‚àÄ (g : C ‚Üí D) ‚Üí ‚àÄ xs ys ‚Üí
                map g (zipWith f xs ys) ‚â°
                zipWith (Œª x y ‚Üí g (f x y)) xs ys
  map-zipWith g []       []       = refl
  map-zipWith g []       (y ‚à∑ ys) = refl
  map-zipWith g (x ‚à∑ xs) []       = refl
  map-zipWith g (x ‚à∑ xs) (y ‚à∑ ys) =
    cong‚ÇÇ _‚à∑_ refl (map-zipWith g xs ys)
 
  zipWith-flip : ‚àÄ xs ys ‚Üí zipWith f xs ys ‚â° zipWith (flip f) ys xs
  zipWith-flip []       []       = refl
  zipWith-flip []       (x ‚à∑ ys) = refl
  zipWith-flip (x ‚à∑ xs) []       = refl
  zipWith-flip (x ‚à∑ xs) (y ‚à∑ ys) = cong (f x y ‚à∑_) (zipWith-flip xs ys)
 
module _ (f : A ‚Üí A ‚Üí B) where
 
  zipWith-comm : (‚àÄ x y ‚Üí f x y ‚â° f y x) ‚Üí
                 ‚àÄ xs ys ‚Üí zipWith f xs ys ‚â° zipWith f ys xs
  zipWith-comm f-comm xs ys = begin
    zipWith f xs ys        ‚â°‚ü® zipWith-flip f xs ys ‚ü©
    zipWith (flip f) ys xs ‚â°‚ü® zipWith-cong (flip f-comm) ys xs ‚ü©
    zipWith f ys xs        ‚àé
 
------------------------------------------------------------------------
-- zip
 
zip-map : ‚àÄ (f : A ‚Üí B) (g : C ‚Üí D) ‚Üí
          ‚àÄ xs ys ‚Üí zip (map f xs) (map g ys) ‚â°
                    map (Product.map f g) (zip xs ys)
zip-map f g xs ys = begin
  zip (map f xs) (map g ys)         ‚â°‚ü® zipWith-map _,_ f g xs ys ‚ü©
  zipWith (Œª x y ‚Üí f x , g y) xs ys ‚â°‚ü® sym (map-zipWith _,_ (Product.map f g) xs ys) ‚ü©
  map (Product.map f g) (zip xs ys) ‚àé
 
zip-flip : ‚àÄ (xs : List A) (ys : List B) ‚Üí
           zip xs ys ‚â° map Product.swap (zip ys xs)
zip-flip xs ys = begin
  zip xs ys                    ‚â°‚ü® zipWith-flip _,_ xs ys ‚ü©
  zipWith (flip _,_) ys xs     ‚â°‚ü® sym (map-zipWith _,_ Product.swap ys xs) ‚ü©
  map Product.swap (zip ys xs) ‚àé

-- unalignWith
 
unalignWith-this : unalignWith ((A ‚Üí These A B) ‚àã this) ‚âó (_, [])
unalignWith-this []       = refl
unalignWith-this (a ‚à∑ as) = cong (Product.map‚ÇÅ (a ‚à∑_)) (unalignWith-this as)
 
unalignWith-that : unalignWith ((B ‚Üí These A B) ‚àã that) ‚âó ([] ,_)
unalignWith-that []       = refl
unalignWith-that (b ‚à∑ bs) = cong (Product.map‚ÇÇ (b ‚à∑_)) (unalignWith-that bs)
 
module _ {f g : C ‚Üí These A B} where
 
  unalignWith-cong : f ‚âó g ‚Üí unalignWith f ‚âó unalignWith g
  unalignWith-cong f‚âóg []       = refl
  unalignWith-cong f‚âóg (c ‚à∑ cs) with f c | g c | f‚âóg c
  ... | this a    | ._ | refl = cong (Product.map‚ÇÅ (a ‚à∑_)) (unalignWith-cong f‚âóg cs)
  ... | that b    | ._ | refl = cong (Product.map‚ÇÇ (b ‚à∑_)) (unalignWith-cong f‚âóg cs)
  ... | these a b | ._ | refl = cong (Product.map (a ‚à∑_) (b ‚à∑_)) (unalignWith-cong f‚âóg cs)
 
module _ (f : C ‚Üí These A B) where
 
  unalignWith-map : (g : D ‚Üí C) ‚Üí ‚àÄ ds ‚Üí
                    unalignWith f (map g ds) ‚â° unalignWith (f ‚àò‚Ä≤ g) ds
  unalignWith-map g []       = refl
  unalignWith-map g (d ‚à∑ ds) with f (g d)
  ... | this a    = cong (Product.map‚ÇÅ (a ‚à∑_)) (unalignWith-map g ds)
  ... | that b    = cong (Product.map‚ÇÇ (b ‚à∑_)) (unalignWith-map g ds)
  ... | these a b = cong (Product.map (a ‚à∑_) (b ‚à∑_)) (unalignWith-map g ds)
 
  map-unalignWith : (g : A ‚Üí D) (h : B ‚Üí E) ‚Üí
    Product.map (map g) (map h) ‚àò‚Ä≤ unalignWith f ‚âó unalignWith (These.map g h ‚àò‚Ä≤ f)
  map-unalignWith g h []       = refl
  map-unalignWith g h (c ‚à∑ cs) with f c
  ... | this a    = cong (Product.map‚ÇÅ (g a ‚à∑_)) (map-unalignWith g h cs)
  ... | that b    = cong (Product.map‚ÇÇ (h b ‚à∑_)) (map-unalignWith g h cs)
  ... | these a b = cong (Product.map (g a ‚à∑_) (h b ‚à∑_)) (map-unalignWith g h cs)
 
  unalignWith-alignWith : (g : These A B ‚Üí C) ‚Üí f ‚àò‚Ä≤ g ‚âó id ‚Üí ‚àÄ as bs ‚Üí
                          unalignWith f (alignWith g as bs) ‚â° (as , bs)
  unalignWith-alignWith g g‚àòf‚âóid []         bs = begin
    unalignWith f (map (g ‚àò‚Ä≤ that) bs) ‚â°‚ü® unalignWith-map (g ‚àò‚Ä≤ that) bs ‚ü©
    unalignWith (f ‚àò‚Ä≤ g ‚àò‚Ä≤ that) bs    ‚â°‚ü® unalignWith-cong (g‚àòf‚âóid ‚àò that) bs ‚ü©
    unalignWith that bs                ‚â°‚ü® unalignWith-that bs ‚ü©
    [] , bs                            ‚àé
  unalignWith-alignWith g g‚àòf‚âóid as@(_ ‚à∑ _) [] = begin
    unalignWith f (map (g ‚àò‚Ä≤ this) as) ‚â°‚ü® unalignWith-map (g ‚àò‚Ä≤ this) as ‚ü©
    unalignWith (f ‚àò‚Ä≤ g ‚àò‚Ä≤ this) as    ‚â°‚ü® unalignWith-cong (g‚àòf‚âóid ‚àò this) as ‚ü©
    unalignWith this as                ‚â°‚ü® unalignWith-this as ‚ü©
    as , []                            ‚àé
  unalignWith-alignWith g g‚àòf‚âóid (a ‚à∑ as)   (b ‚à∑ bs)
    rewrite g‚àòf‚âóid (these a b) =
    cong (Product.map (a ‚à∑_) (b ‚à∑_)) (unalignWith-alignWith g g‚àòf‚âóid as bs)

-- unzipWith
 
module _ {f g : A ‚Üí B √ó C} where
 
  unzipWith-cong : f ‚âó g ‚Üí unzipWith f ‚âó unzipWith g
  unzipWith-cong f‚âóg [] = refl
  unzipWith-cong f‚âóg (x ‚à∑ xs) =
    cong‚ÇÇ (Product.zip _‚à∑_ _‚à∑_) (f‚âóg x) (unzipWith-cong f‚âóg xs)
 
module _ (f : A ‚Üí B √ó C) where
 
  length-unzipWith‚ÇÅ : ‚àÄ xys ‚Üí
                     length (proj‚ÇÅ (unzipWith f xys)) ‚â° length xys
  length-unzipWith‚ÇÅ []        = refl
  length-unzipWith‚ÇÅ (x ‚à∑ xys) = cong suc (length-unzipWith‚ÇÅ xys)
 
  length-unzipWith‚ÇÇ : ‚àÄ xys ‚Üí
                     length (proj‚ÇÇ (unzipWith f xys)) ‚â° length xys
  length-unzipWith‚ÇÇ []        = refl
  length-unzipWith‚ÇÇ (x ‚à∑ xys) = cong suc (length-unzipWith‚ÇÇ xys)
 
  zipWith-unzipWith : (g : B ‚Üí C ‚Üí A) ‚Üí uncurry‚Ä≤ g ‚àò f ‚âó id ‚Üí
                      uncurry‚Ä≤ (zipWith g) ‚àò (unzipWith f)  ‚âó id
  zipWith-unzipWith g g‚àòf‚âóid []       = refl
  zipWith-unzipWith g g‚àòf‚âóid (x ‚à∑ xs) =
    cong‚ÇÇ _‚à∑_ (g‚àòf‚âóid x) (zipWith-unzipWith g g‚àòf‚âóid xs)
 
  unzipWith-zipWith : (g : B ‚Üí C ‚Üí A) ‚Üí f ‚àò uncurry‚Ä≤ g ‚âó id ‚Üí
                      ‚àÄ xs ys ‚Üí length xs ‚â° length ys ‚Üí
                      unzipWith f (zipWith g xs ys) ‚â° (xs , ys)
  unzipWith-zipWith g f‚àòg‚âóid []       []       l‚â°l = refl
  unzipWith-zipWith g f‚àòg‚âóid (x ‚à∑ xs) (y ‚à∑ ys) l‚â°l  =
    cong‚ÇÇ (Product.zip _‚à∑_ _‚à∑_) (f‚àòg‚âóid (x , y))
          (unzipWith-zipWith g f‚àòg‚âóid xs ys (suc-injective l‚â°l))
 
  unzipWith-map : (g : D ‚Üí A) ‚Üí unzipWith f ‚àò map g ‚âó unzipWith (f ‚àò g)
  unzipWith-map g []       = refl
  unzipWith-map g (x ‚à∑ xs) =
    cong (Product.zip _‚à∑_ _‚à∑_ (f (g x))) (unzipWith-map g xs)
 
  map-unzipWith : (g : B ‚Üí D) (h : C ‚Üí E) ‚Üí
                  Product.map (map g) (map h) ‚àò unzipWith f ‚âó
                  unzipWith (Product.map g h ‚àò f)
  map-unzipWith g h []       = refl
  map-unzipWith g h (x ‚à∑ xs) =
    cong (Product.zip _‚à∑_ _‚à∑_ _) (map-unzipWith g h xs)
 
  unzipWith-swap : unzipWith (Product.swap ‚àò f) ‚âó
                   Product.swap ‚àò unzipWith f
  unzipWith-swap []       = refl
  unzipWith-swap (x ‚à∑ xs) =
    cong (Product.zip _‚à∑_ _‚à∑_ _) (unzipWith-swap xs)
 
  unzipWith-++ : ‚àÄ xs ys ‚Üí
                 unzipWith f (xs ++ ys) ‚â°
                 Product.zip _++_ _++_ (unzipWith f xs) (unzipWith f ys)
  unzipWith-++ []       ys = refl
  unzipWith-++ (x ‚à∑ xs) ys =
    cong (Product.zip _‚à∑_ _‚à∑_ (f x)) (unzipWith-++ xs ys)

-- unzip
 
unzip-map : ‚àÄ (f : A ‚Üí B) (g : C ‚Üí D) ‚Üí
            unzip ‚àò map (Product.map f g) ‚âó
            Product.map (map f) (map g) ‚àò unzip
unzip-map f g xs = begin
  unzip (map (Product.map f g) xs)       ‚â°‚ü® unzipWith-map id (Product.map f g) xs ‚ü©
  unzipWith (Product.map f g) xs         ‚â°‚ü® sym (map-unzipWith id f g xs) ‚ü©
  Product.map (map f) (map g) (unzip xs) ‚àé
 
unzip-swap : unzip ‚àò map Product.swap ‚âó Product.swap ‚àò unzip {A = A} {B = B}
unzip-swap xs = begin
  unzip (map Product.swap xs) ‚â°‚ü® unzipWith-map id Product.swap xs ‚ü©
  unzipWith Product.swap xs   ‚â°‚ü® unzipWith-swap id xs ‚ü©
  Product.swap (unzip xs)     ‚àé
 
zip-unzip : uncurry‚Ä≤ zip ‚àò unzip ‚âó id {A = List (A √ó B)}
zip-unzip = zipWith-unzipWith id _,_ Œª _ ‚Üí refl
 
unzip-zip : ‚àÄ (xs : List A) (ys : List B) ‚Üí
            length xs ‚â° length ys ‚Üí unzip (zip xs ys) ‚â° (xs , ys)
unzip-zip = unzipWith-zipWith id _,_ Œª _ ‚Üí refl

-- foldr
 
foldr-universal : ‚àÄ (h : List A ‚Üí B) f e ‚Üí (h [] ‚â° e) ‚Üí
                  (‚àÄ x xs ‚Üí h (x ‚à∑ xs) ‚â° f x (h xs)) ‚Üí
                  h ‚âó foldr f e
foldr-universal h f e base step []       = base
foldr-universal h f e base step (x ‚à∑ xs) = begin
  h (x ‚à∑ xs)          ‚â°‚ü® step x xs ‚ü©
  f x (h xs)          ‚â°‚ü® cong (f x) (foldr-universal h f e base step xs) ‚ü©
  f x (foldr f e xs)  ‚àé
 
foldr-cong : ‚àÄ {f g : A ‚Üí B ‚Üí B} {d e : B} ‚Üí
             (‚àÄ x y ‚Üí f x y ‚â° g x y) ‚Üí d ‚â° e ‚Üí
             foldr f d ‚âó foldr g e
foldr-cong f‚âóg refl []      = refl
foldr-cong f‚âóg d‚â°e (x ‚à∑ xs) rewrite foldr-cong f‚âóg d‚â°e xs = f‚âóg x _
 
foldr-fusion : ‚àÄ (h : B ‚Üí C) {f : A ‚Üí B ‚Üí B} {g : A ‚Üí C ‚Üí C} (e : B) ‚Üí
               (‚àÄ x y ‚Üí h (f x y) ‚â° g x (h y)) ‚Üí
               h ‚àò foldr f e ‚âó foldr g (h e)
foldr-fusion h {f} {g} e fuse =
  foldr-universal (h ‚àò foldr f e) g (h e) refl
                  (Œª x xs ‚Üí fuse x (foldr f e xs))
 
id-is-foldr : id {A = List A} ‚âó foldr _‚à∑_ []
id-is-foldr = foldr-universal id _‚à∑_ [] refl (Œª _ _ ‚Üí refl)
 
++-is-foldr : (xs ys : List A) ‚Üí xs ++ ys ‚â° foldr _‚à∑_ ys xs
++-is-foldr xs ys = begin
  xs ++ ys                ‚â°‚ü® cong (_++ ys) (id-is-foldr xs) ‚ü©
  foldr _‚à∑_ [] xs ++ ys   ‚â°‚ü® foldr-fusion (_++ ys) [] (Œª _ _ ‚Üí refl) xs ‚ü©
  foldr _‚à∑_ ([] ++ ys) xs ‚â°‚ü®‚ü©
  foldr _‚à∑_ ys xs         ‚àé
 
foldr-++ : ‚àÄ (f : A ‚Üí B ‚Üí B) x ys zs ‚Üí
           foldr f x (ys ++ zs) ‚â° foldr f (foldr f x zs) ys
foldr-++ f x []       zs = refl
foldr-++ f x (y ‚à∑ ys) zs = cong (f y) (foldr-++ f x ys zs)
 
map-is-foldr : {f : A ‚Üí B} ‚Üí map f ‚âó foldr (Œª x ys ‚Üí f x ‚à∑ ys) []
map-is-foldr {f = f} xs = begin
  map f xs                        ‚â°‚ü® cong (map f) (id-is-foldr xs) ‚ü©
  map f (foldr _‚à∑_ [] xs)         ‚â°‚ü® foldr-fusion (map f) [] (Œª _ _ ‚Üí refl) xs ‚ü©
  foldr (Œª x ys ‚Üí f x ‚à∑ ys) [] xs ‚àé
 
foldr-‚à∑ ≥ : ‚àÄ (f : A ‚Üí B ‚Üí B) x y ys ‚Üí
           foldr f x (ys ‚à∑ ≥ y) ‚â° foldr f (f y x) ys
foldr-‚à∑ ≥ f x y []       = refl
foldr-‚à∑ ≥ f x y (z ‚à∑ ys) = cong (f z) (foldr-‚à∑ ≥ f x y ys)
 
foldr-map : ‚àÄ (f : A ‚Üí B ‚Üí B) (g : C ‚Üí A) x xs ‚Üí foldr f x (map g xs) ‚â° foldr (g -‚ü® f ‚à£) x xs
foldr-map f g x []       = refl
foldr-map f g x (y ‚à∑ xs) = cong (f (g y)) (foldr-map f g x xs)
 
-- Interaction with predicates
 
module _ {P : Pred A p} {f : A ‚Üí A ‚Üí A} where
 
  foldr-forces·µá : (‚àÄ x y ‚Üí P (f x y) ‚Üí P x √ó P y) ‚Üí
                  ‚àÄ e xs ‚Üí P (foldr f e xs) ‚Üí All P xs
  foldr-forces·µá _      _ []       _     = []
  foldr-forces·µá forces _ (x ‚à∑ xs) Pfold =
    let px , pfxs = forces _ _ Pfold in px ‚à∑ foldr-forces·µá forces _ xs pfxs
 
  foldr-preserves·µá : (‚àÄ {x y} ‚Üí P x ‚Üí P y ‚Üí P (f x y)) ‚Üí
                     ‚àÄ {e xs} ‚Üí P e ‚Üí All P xs ‚Üí P (foldr f e xs)
  foldr-preserves·µá _    Pe []         = Pe
  foldr-preserves·µá pres Pe (px ‚à∑ pxs) = pres px (foldr-preserves·µá pres Pe pxs)
 
  foldr-preserves ≥ : (‚àÄ x {y} ‚Üí P y ‚Üí P (f x y)) ‚Üí
                     ‚àÄ {e} ‚Üí P e ‚Üí ‚àÄ xs ‚Üí P (foldr f e xs)
  foldr-preserves ≥ pres Pe []       = Pe
  foldr-preserves ≥ pres Pe (_ ‚à∑ xs) = pres _ (foldr-preserves ≥ pres Pe xs)
 
  foldr-preserves·µí : (‚àÄ x y ‚Üí P x ‚äé P y ‚Üí P (f x y)) ‚Üí
                     ‚àÄ e xs ‚Üí P e ‚äé Any P xs ‚Üí P (foldr f e xs)
  foldr-preserves·µí pres e []       (inj‚ÇÅ Pe)          = Pe
  foldr-preserves·µí pres e (x ‚à∑ xs) (inj‚ÇÅ Pe)          =
    pres _ _ (inj‚ÇÇ (foldr-preserves·µí pres e xs (inj‚ÇÅ Pe)))
  foldr-preserves·µí pres e (x ‚à∑ xs) (inj‚ÇÇ (here px))   = pres _ _ (inj‚ÇÅ px)
  foldr-preserves·µí pres e (x ‚à∑ xs) (inj‚ÇÇ (there pxs)) =
    pres _ _ (inj‚ÇÇ (foldr-preserves·µí pres e xs (inj‚ÇÇ pxs)))
 
------------------------------------------------------------------------
-- foldl
 
foldl-cong : ‚àÄ {f g : B ‚Üí A ‚Üí B} ‚Üí (‚àÄ x y ‚Üí f x y ‚â° g x y) ‚Üí
             ‚àÄ x ‚Üí foldl f x ‚âó foldl g x
foldl-cong f‚âóg x []       = refl
foldl-cong f‚âóg x (y ‚à∑ xs) rewrite f‚âóg x y = foldl-cong f‚âóg _ xs
 
foldl-++ : ‚àÄ (f : A ‚Üí B ‚Üí A) x ys zs ‚Üí
           foldl f x (ys ++ zs) ‚â° foldl f (foldl f x ys) zs
foldl-++ f x []       zs = refl
foldl-++ f x (y ‚à∑ ys) zs = foldl-++ f (f x y) ys zs
 
foldl-‚à∑ ≥ : ‚àÄ (f : A ‚Üí B ‚Üí A) x y ys ‚Üí
           foldl f x (ys ‚à∑ ≥ y) ‚â° f (foldl f x ys) y
foldl-‚à∑ ≥ f x y []       = refl
foldl-‚à∑ ≥ f x y (z ‚à∑ ys) = foldl-‚à∑ ≥ f (f x z) y ys
 
foldl-map : ‚àÄ (f : A ‚Üí B ‚Üí A) (g : C ‚Üí B) x xs ‚Üí foldl f x (map g xs) ‚â° foldl (‚à£ f ‚ü©- g) x xs
foldl-map f g x []       = refl
foldl-map f g x (y ‚à∑ xs) = foldl-map f g (f x (g y)) xs
 
------------------------------------------------------------------------
-- concat
 
concat-map : ‚àÄ {f : A ‚Üí B} ‚Üí concat ‚àò map (map f) ‚âó map f ‚àò concat
concat-map {f = f} xss = begin
  concat (map (map f) xss)                   ‚â°‚ü® cong concat (map-is-foldr xss) ‚ü©
  concat (foldr (Œª xs ‚Üí map f xs ‚à∑_) [] xss) ‚â°‚ü® foldr-fusion concat [] (Œª _ _ ‚Üí refl) xss ‚ü©
  foldr (Œª ys ‚Üí map f ys ++_) [] xss         ‚â°‚ü® sym (foldr-fusion (map f) [] (map-++ f) xss) ‚ü©
  map f (concat xss)                         ‚àé
 
concat-++ : (xss yss : List (List A)) ‚Üí concat xss ++ concat yss ‚â° concat (xss ++ yss)
concat-++ [] yss = refl
concat-++ ([] ‚à∑ xss) yss = concat-++ xss yss
concat-++ ((x ‚à∑ xs) ‚à∑ xss) yss = cong (x ‚à∑_) (concat-++ (xs ‚à∑ xss) yss)
 
concat-concat : concat {A = A} ‚àò map concat ‚âó concat ‚àò concat
concat-concat [] = refl
concat-concat (xss ‚à∑ xsss) = begin
  concat (map concat (xss ‚à∑ xsss))   ‚â°‚ü® cong (concat xss ++_) (concat-concat xsss) ‚ü©
  concat xss ++ concat (concat xsss) ‚â°‚ü® concat-++ xss (concat xsss) ‚ü©
  concat (concat (xss ‚à∑ xsss))       ‚àé
 
concat-[-] : concat {A = A} ‚àò map [_] ‚âó id
concat-[-] [] = refl
concat-[-] (x ‚à∑ xs) = cong (x ‚à∑_) (concat-[-] xs)
 
------------------------------------------------------------------------
-- concatMap
 
concatMap-cong : ‚àÄ {f g : A ‚Üí List B} ‚Üí f ‚âó g ‚Üí concatMap f ‚âó concatMap g
concatMap-cong eq xs = cong concat (map-cong eq xs)
 
concatMap-pure : concatMap {A = A} [_] ‚âó id
concatMap-pure = concat-[-]
 
concatMap-map : (g : B ‚Üí List C) ‚Üí (f : A ‚Üí B) ‚Üí (xs : List A) ‚Üí
                concatMap g (map f xs) ‚â° concatMap (g ‚àò‚Ä≤ f) xs
concatMap-map g f xs
  = cong concat
      {x = map g (map f xs)}
      {y = map (g ‚àò‚Ä≤ f) xs}
      (sym $ map-‚àò xs)
 
map-concatMap : (f : B ‚Üí C) (g : A ‚Üí List B) ‚Üí
                map f ‚àò‚Ä≤ concatMap g ‚âó concatMap (map f ‚àò‚Ä≤ g)
map-concatMap f g xs = begin
  map f (concatMap g xs)
    ‚â°‚ü®‚ü©
  map f (concat (map g xs))
    ‚â°‚ü® concat-map (map g xs) ‚ü®
  concat (map (map f) (map g xs))
    ‚â°‚ü® cong concat
         {x = map (map f) (map g xs)}
         {y = map (map f ‚àò‚Ä≤ g) xs}
         (sym $ map-‚àò xs) ‚ü©
  concat (map (map f ‚àò‚Ä≤ g) xs)
    ‚â°‚ü®‚ü©
  concatMap (map f ‚àò‚Ä≤ g) xs
    ‚àé

-- catMaybes
 
catMaybes-concatMap : catMaybes {A = A} ‚âó concatMap fromMaybe
catMaybes-concatMap []             = refl
catMaybes-concatMap (just x  ‚à∑ xs) = cong (x ‚à∑_) $ catMaybes-concatMap xs
catMaybes-concatMap (nothing ‚à∑ xs) = catMaybes-concatMap xs
 
length-catMaybes : ‚àÄ xs ‚Üí length (catMaybes {A = A} xs) ‚â§ length xs
length-catMaybes []             = ‚â§-refl
length-catMaybes (just _  ‚à∑ xs) = s‚â§s $ length-catMaybes xs
length-catMaybes (nothing ‚à∑ xs) = m‚â§n‚áím‚â§1+n $ length-catMaybes xs
 
catMaybes-++ : (xs ys : List (Maybe A)) ‚Üí
               catMaybes (xs ++ ys) ‚â° catMaybes xs ++ catMaybes ys
catMaybes-++ []             _  = refl
catMaybes-++ (just x  ‚à∑ xs) ys = cong (x ‚à∑_) $ catMaybes-++ xs ys
catMaybes-++ (nothing ‚à∑ xs) ys = catMaybes-++ xs ys
 
map-catMaybes : (f : A ‚Üí B) ‚Üí map f ‚àò catMaybes ‚âó catMaybes ‚àò map (Maybe.map f)
map-catMaybes _ []             = refl
map-catMaybes f (just x  ‚à∑ xs) = cong (f x ‚à∑_) $ map-catMaybes f xs
map-catMaybes f (nothing ‚à∑ xs) = map-catMaybes f xs
 
Any-catMaybes‚Å∫ : ‚àÄ {P : Pred A ‚Ñì} {xs : List (Maybe A)} ‚Üí
                 Any (MAny P) xs ‚Üí Any P (catMaybes xs)
Any-catMaybes‚Å∫ {xs = nothing ‚à∑ xs} (there x‚àà)       = Any-catMaybes‚Å∫ x‚àà
Any-catMaybes‚Å∫ {xs = just x  ‚à∑ xs} (here (just px)) = here px
Any-catMaybes‚Å∫ {xs = just x  ‚à∑ xs} (there x‚àà)       = there $ Any-catMaybes‚Å∫ x‚àà

-- mapMaybe
 
mapMaybe-cong : {f g : A ‚Üí Maybe B} ‚Üí f ‚âó g ‚Üí mapMaybe f ‚âó mapMaybe g
mapMaybe-cong f‚âóg = cong catMaybes ‚àò map-cong f‚âóg
 
mapMaybe-just : (xs : List A) ‚Üí mapMaybe just xs ‚â° xs
mapMaybe-just []       = refl
mapMaybe-just (x ‚à∑ xs) = cong (x ‚à∑_) (mapMaybe-just xs)
 
mapMaybe-nothing : (xs : List A) ‚Üí
                   mapMaybe {B = B} (Œª _ ‚Üí nothing) xs ‚â° []
mapMaybe-nothing []       = refl
mapMaybe-nothing (x ‚à∑ xs) = mapMaybe-nothing xs
 
module _ (f : A ‚Üí Maybe B) where
 
  mapMaybe-concatMap : mapMaybe f ‚âó concatMap (fromMaybe ‚àò f)
  mapMaybe-concatMap xs = begin
    catMaybes (map f xs)            ‚â°‚ü® catMaybes-concatMap (map f xs) ‚ü©
    concatMap fromMaybe (map f xs)  ‚â°‚ü® concatMap-map fromMaybe f xs ‚ü©
    concatMap (fromMaybe ‚àò f) xs    ‚àé
 
  length-mapMaybe : ‚àÄ xs ‚Üí length (mapMaybe f xs) ‚â§ length xs
  length-mapMaybe xs = ‚â§-begin
    length (mapMaybe f xs)      ‚â§‚ü® length-catMaybes (map f xs) ‚ü©
    length (map f xs)           ‚â§‚ü® ‚â§-reflexive (length-map f xs) ‚ü©
    length xs                   ‚â§-‚àé
    where open ‚â§-Reasoning renaming (begin_ to ‚â§-begin_; _‚àé to _‚â§-‚àé)
 
  mapMaybe-++ : ‚àÄ xs ys ‚Üí
                mapMaybe f (xs ++ ys) ‚â° mapMaybe f xs ++ mapMaybe f ys
  mapMaybe-++ xs ys = begin
    catMaybes (map f (xs ++ ys))     ‚â°‚ü® cong catMaybes (map-++ f xs ys) ‚ü©
    catMaybes (map f xs ++ map f ys) ‚â°‚ü® catMaybes-++ (map f xs) (map f ys) ‚ü©
    mapMaybe f xs ++ mapMaybe f ys   ‚àé
 
module _ (f : B ‚Üí Maybe C) (g : A ‚Üí B) where
 
  mapMaybe-map : mapMaybe f ‚àò map g ‚âó mapMaybe (f ‚àò g)
  mapMaybe-map = cong catMaybes ‚àò sym ‚àò map-‚àò
 
module _ (g : B ‚Üí C) (f : A ‚Üí Maybe B) where
 
  map-mapMaybe : map g ‚àò mapMaybe f ‚âó mapMaybe (Maybe.map g ‚àò f)
  map-mapMaybe xs = begin
    map g (catMaybes (map f xs))       ‚â°‚ü® map-catMaybes g (map f xs) ‚ü©
    mapMaybe (Maybe.map g) (map f xs)  ‚â°‚ü® mapMaybe-map _ f xs ‚ü©
    mapMaybe (Maybe.map g ‚àò f) xs      ‚àé
 
-- embedding-projection pairs
module _ {proj : B ‚Üí Maybe A} {emb : A ‚Üí B} where
  mapMaybe-map-retract : proj ‚àò emb ‚âó just ‚Üí mapMaybe proj ‚àò map emb ‚âó id
  mapMaybe-map-retract retract xs = begin
    mapMaybe proj (map emb xs) ‚â°‚ü® mapMaybe-map _ _ xs ‚ü©
    mapMaybe (proj ‚àò emb) xs   ‚â°‚ü® mapMaybe-cong retract xs ‚ü©
    mapMaybe just xs           ‚â°‚ü® mapMaybe-just _ ‚ü©
    xs                         ‚àé
 
module _ {proj : C ‚Üí Maybe B} {emb : A ‚Üí C} where
  mapMaybe-map-none : proj ‚àò emb ‚âó const nothing ‚Üí mapMaybe proj ‚àò map emb ‚âó const []
  mapMaybe-map-none retract xs = begin
    mapMaybe proj (map emb xs)  ‚â°‚ü® mapMaybe-map _ _ xs ‚ü©
    mapMaybe (proj ‚àò emb) xs    ‚â°‚ü® mapMaybe-cong retract xs ‚ü©
    mapMaybe (const nothing) xs ‚â°‚ü® mapMaybe-nothing xs ‚ü©
    []                          ‚àé
 
-- embedding-projection pairs on sums
mapMaybeIsInj‚ÇÅ‚àòmapInj‚ÇÅ : (xs : List A) ‚Üí mapMaybe (isInj‚ÇÅ {B = B}) (map inj‚ÇÅ xs) ‚â° xs
mapMaybeIsInj‚ÇÅ‚àòmapInj‚ÇÅ = mapMaybe-map-retract Œª _ ‚Üí refl
 
mapMaybeIsInj‚ÇÅ‚àòmapInj‚ÇÇ : (xs : List B) ‚Üí mapMaybe (isInj‚ÇÅ {A = A}) (map inj‚ÇÇ xs) ‚â° []
mapMaybeIsInj‚ÇÅ‚àòmapInj‚ÇÇ = mapMaybe-map-none Œª _ ‚Üí refl
 
mapMaybeIsInj‚ÇÇ‚àòmapInj‚ÇÇ : (xs : List B) ‚Üí mapMaybe (isInj‚ÇÇ {A = A}) (map inj‚ÇÇ xs) ‚â° xs
mapMaybeIsInj‚ÇÇ‚àòmapInj‚ÇÇ = mapMaybe-map-retract Œª _ ‚Üí refl
 
mapMaybeIsInj‚ÇÇ‚àòmapInj‚ÇÅ : (xs : List A) ‚Üí mapMaybe (isInj‚ÇÇ {B = B}) (map inj‚ÇÅ xs) ‚â° []
mapMaybeIsInj‚ÇÇ‚àòmapInj‚ÇÅ = mapMaybe-map-none Œª _ ‚Üí refl

-- sum
 
sum-++ : ‚àÄ xs ys ‚Üí sum (xs ++ ys) ‚â° sum xs + sum ys
sum-++ []       ys = refl
sum-++ (x ‚à∑ xs) ys = begin
  x + sum (xs ++ ys)     ‚â°‚ü® cong (x +_) (sum-++ xs ys) ‚ü©
  x + (sum xs + sum ys)  ‚â°‚ü® sym (+-assoc x _ _) ‚ü©
  (x + sum xs) + sum ys  ‚àé

-- product
 
‚àà‚áí‚à£product : ‚àÄ {n ns} ‚Üí n ‚àà ns ‚Üí n ‚à£ product ns
‚àà‚áí‚à£product {n} {n ‚à∑ ns} (here  refl) = divides (product ns) (*-comm n (product ns))
‚àà‚áí‚à£product {n} {m ‚à∑ ns} (there n‚ààns) = ‚à£n‚áí‚à£m*n m (‚àà‚áí‚à£product n‚ààns)

-- applyUpTo
 
length-applyUpTo : ‚àÄ (f : ‚Ñï ‚Üí A) n ‚Üí length (applyUpTo f n) ‚â° n
length-applyUpTo f zero    = refl
length-applyUpTo f (suc n) = cong suc (length-applyUpTo (f ‚àò suc) n)
 
lookup-applyUpTo : ‚àÄ (f : ‚Ñï ‚Üí A) n i ‚Üí lookup (applyUpTo f n) i ‚â° f (to‚Ñï i)
lookup-applyUpTo f (suc n) zero    = refl
lookup-applyUpTo f (suc n) (suc i) = lookup-applyUpTo (f ‚àò suc) n i
 
applyUpTo-‚à∑ ≥ : ‚àÄ (f : ‚Ñï ‚Üí A) n ‚Üí applyUpTo f n ‚à∑ ≥ f n ‚â° applyUpTo f (suc n)
applyUpTo-‚à∑ ≥ f zero = refl
applyUpTo-‚à∑ ≥ f (suc n) = cong (f 0 ‚à∑_) (applyUpTo-‚à∑ ≥ (f ‚àò suc) n)
 
------------------------------------------------------------------------
-- applyDownFrom
 
module _ (f : ‚Ñï ‚Üí A) where
 
  length-applyDownFrom : ‚àÄ n ‚Üí length (applyDownFrom f n) ‚â° n
  length-applyDownFrom zero    = refl
  length-applyDownFrom (suc n) = cong suc (length-applyDownFrom n)
 
  lookup-applyDownFrom : ‚àÄ n i ‚Üí lookup (applyDownFrom f n) i ‚â° f (n ‚à∏ (suc (to‚Ñï i)))
  lookup-applyDownFrom (suc n) zero    = refl
  lookup-applyDownFrom (suc n) (suc i) = lookup-applyDownFrom n i
 
  applyDownFrom-‚à∑ ≥ : ‚àÄ n ‚Üí applyDownFrom (f ‚àò suc) n ‚à∑ ≥ f 0 ‚â° applyDownFrom f (suc n)
  applyDownFrom-‚à∑ ≥ zero = refl
  applyDownFrom-‚à∑ ≥ (suc n) = cong (f (suc n) ‚à∑_) (applyDownFrom-‚à∑ ≥ n)

-- upTo
 
length-upTo : ‚àÄ n ‚Üí length (upTo n) ‚â° n
length-upTo = length-applyUpTo id
 
lookup-upTo : ‚àÄ n i ‚Üí lookup (upTo n) i ‚â° to‚Ñï i
lookup-upTo = lookup-applyUpTo id
 
upTo-‚à∑ ≥ : ‚àÄ n ‚Üí upTo n ‚à∑ ≥ n ‚â° upTo (suc n)
upTo-‚à∑ ≥ = applyUpTo-‚à∑ ≥ id

-- downFrom
 
length-downFrom : ‚àÄ n ‚Üí length (downFrom n) ‚â° n

lookup-downFrom : ‚àÄ n i ‚Üí lookup (downFrom n) i ‚â° n ‚à∏ (suc (to‚Ñï i))
lookup-downFrom = lookup-applyDownFrom id
 
downFrom-‚à∑ ≥ : ‚àÄ n ‚Üí applyDownFrom suc n ‚à∑ ≥ 0 ‚â° downFrom (suc n)
downFrom-‚à∑ ≥ = applyDownFrom-‚à∑ ≥ id

-- tabulate
 
tabulate-cong : ‚àÄ {n} {f g : Fin n ‚Üí A} ‚Üí
                f ‚âó g ‚Üí tabulate f ‚â° tabulate g
tabulate-cong {n = zero}  p = refl
tabulate-cong {n = suc n} p = cong‚ÇÇ _‚à∑_ (p zero) (tabulate-cong (p ‚àò suc))
 
tabulate-lookup : ‚àÄ (xs : List A) ‚Üí tabulate (lookup xs) ‚â° xs
tabulate-lookup []       = refl
tabulate-lookup (x ‚à∑ xs) = cong (_ ‚à∑_) (tabulate-lookup xs)
 
length-tabulate : ‚àÄ {n} ‚Üí (f : Fin n ‚Üí A) ‚Üí
                  length (tabulate f) ‚â° n
length-tabulate {n = zero} f = refl
length-tabulate {n = suc n} f = cong suc (length-tabulate (Œª z ‚Üí f (suc z)))
 
lookup-tabulate : ‚àÄ {n} ‚Üí (f : Fin n ‚Üí A) ‚Üí
                  ‚àÄ i ‚Üí let i‚Ä≤ = cast (sym (length-tabulate f)) i
                        in lookup (tabulate f) i‚Ä≤ ‚â° f i
lookup-tabulate f zero    = refl
lookup-tabulate f (suc i) = lookup-tabulate (f ‚àò suc) i
 
map-tabulate : ‚àÄ {n} (g : Fin n ‚Üí A) (f : A ‚Üí B) ‚Üí
               map f (tabulate g) ‚â° tabulate (f ‚àò g)
map-tabulate {n = zero}  g f = refl
map-tabulate {n = suc n} g f = cong (_ ‚à∑_) (map-tabulate (g ‚àò suc) f)
 
------------------------------------------------------------------------
-- _[_]%=_
 
length-%= : ‚àÄ xs k (f : A ‚Üí A) ‚Üí length (xs [ k ]%= f) ‚â° length xs
length-%= (x ‚à∑ xs) zero    f = refl
length-%= (x ‚à∑ xs) (suc k) f = cong suc (length-%= xs k f)
 
------------------------------------------------------------------------
-- _[_]‚à∑=_
 
length-‚à∑= : ‚àÄ xs k (v : A) ‚Üí length (xs [ k ]‚à∑= v) ‚â° length xs
length-‚à∑= xs k v = length-%= xs k (const v)
 
map-‚à∑= : ‚àÄ xs k (v : A) (f : A ‚Üí B) ‚Üí
         let eq = sym (length-map f xs) in
         map f (xs [ k ]‚à∑= v) ‚â° map f xs [ cast eq k ]‚à∑= f v
map-‚à∑= (x ‚à∑ xs) zero    v f = refl
map-‚à∑= (x ‚à∑ xs) (suc k) v f = cong (f x ‚à∑_) (map-‚à∑= xs k v f)
 
------------------------------------------------------------------------
-- insertAt
 
length-insertAt : ‚àÄ (xs : List A) (i : Fin (suc (length xs))) v ‚Üí
                  length (insertAt xs i v) ‚â° suc (length xs)
length-insertAt xs       zero    v = refl
length-insertAt (x ‚à∑ xs) (suc i) v = cong suc (length-insertAt xs i v)
 
------------------------------------------------------------------------
-- removeAt
 
length-removeAt : ‚àÄ (xs : List A) k ‚Üí length (removeAt xs k) ‚â° pred (length xs)
length-removeAt (x ‚à∑ xs) zero            = refl
length-removeAt (x ‚à∑ xs@(_ ‚à∑ _)) (suc k) = cong suc (length-removeAt xs k)
 
length-removeAt‚Ä≤ : ‚àÄ (xs : List A) k ‚Üí length xs ‚â° suc (length (removeAt xs k))
length-removeAt‚Ä≤ xs@(_ ‚à∑ _) k rewrite length-removeAt xs k = refl
 
map-removeAt : ‚àÄ xs k (f : A ‚Üí B) ‚Üí
            let eq = sym (length-map f xs) in
            map f (removeAt xs k) ‚â° removeAt (map f xs) (cast eq k)
map-removeAt (x ‚à∑ xs) zero    f = refl
map-removeAt (x ‚à∑ xs) (suc k) f = cong (f x ‚à∑_) (map-removeAt xs k f)
 
------------------------------------------------------------------------
 -- insertAt and removeAt
 
removeAt-insertAt : ‚àÄ (xs : List A) (i : Fin (suc (length xs))) v ‚Üí
  removeAt (insertAt xs i v) ((cast (sym (length-insertAt xs i v)) i)) ‚â° xs
removeAt-insertAt xs       zero    v = refl
removeAt-insertAt (x ‚à∑ xs) (suc i) v = cong (_ ‚à∑_) (removeAt-insertAt xs i v)
 
insertAt-removeAt : (xs : List A) (i : Fin (length xs)) ‚Üí
  insertAt (removeAt xs i) (cast (length-removeAt‚Ä≤ xs i) i) (lookup xs i) ‚â° xs
insertAt-removeAt (x ‚à∑ xs) zero    = refl
insertAt-removeAt (x ‚à∑ xs) (suc i) = cong (x ‚à∑_) (insertAt-removeAt xs i)
 
------------------------------------------------------------------------
-- take
 
length-take : ‚àÄ n (xs : List A) ‚Üí length (take n xs) ‚â° n ‚äì (length xs)
length-take zero    xs       = refl
length-take (suc n) []       = refl
length-take (suc n) (x ‚à∑ xs) = cong suc (length-take n xs)
 
-- Take commutes with map.
take-map : ‚àÄ {f : A ‚Üí B} (n : ‚Ñï) xs ‚Üí take n (map f xs) ‚â° map f (take n xs)
take-map zero xs = refl
take-map (suc s) [] = refl
take-map (suc s) (a ‚à∑ xs) = cong (_ ‚à∑_) (take-map s xs)
 
take-suc : (xs : List A) (i : Fin (length xs)) ‚Üí let m = to‚Ñï i in
           take (suc m) xs ‚â° take m xs ‚à∑ ≥ lookup xs i
take-suc (x ‚à∑ xs) zero    = refl
take-suc (x ‚à∑ xs) (suc i) = cong (x ‚à∑_) (take-suc xs i)
 
take-suc-tabulate : ‚àÄ {n} (f : Fin n ‚Üí A) (i : Fin n) ‚Üí let m = to‚Ñï i in
                    take (suc m) (tabulate f) ‚â° take m (tabulate f) ‚à∑ ≥ f i
take-suc-tabulate f i rewrite sym (to‚Ñï-cast (sym (length-tabulate f)) i) | sym (lookup-tabulate f i)
  = take-suc (tabulate f) (cast _ i)
 
-- If you take at least as many elements from a list as it has, you get
-- the whole list.
take-all : (n : ‚Ñï) (xs : List A) ‚Üí n ‚â• length xs ‚Üí take n xs ‚â° xs
take-all zero [] _ = refl
take-all (suc _) [] _ = refl
take-all (suc n) (x ‚à∑ xs) (s‚â§s pf) = cong (x ‚à∑_) (take-all n xs pf)
 
-- Taking from an empty list does nothing.
take-[] : ‚àÄ m ‚Üí take {A = A} m [] ‚â° []
take-[] zero = refl
take-[] (suc m) = refl
 
-- Taking twice takes the minimum of both counts.
take-take : ‚àÄ n m (xs : List A) ‚Üí take n (take m xs) ‚â° take (n ‚äì m) xs
take-take zero    m       xs       = refl
take-take (suc n) zero    xs       = refl
take-take (suc n) (suc m) []       = refl
take-take (suc n) (suc m) (x ‚à∑ xs) = cong (x ‚à∑_) (take-take n m xs)
 
-- Dropping m elements and then taking n is the same as
-- taking n + m elements and then dropping m.
take-drop : ‚àÄ n m (xs : List A) ‚Üí
            take n (drop m xs) ‚â° drop m (take (m + n) xs)
take-drop n zero    xs       = refl
take-drop n (suc m) []       = take-[] n
take-drop n (suc m) (x ‚à∑ xs) = take-drop n m xs
 
------------------------------------------------------------------------
-- drop
 
length-drop : ‚àÄ n (xs : List A) ‚Üí length (drop n xs) ‚â° length xs ‚à∏ n
length-drop zero    xs       = refl
length-drop (suc n) []       = refl
length-drop (suc n) (x ‚à∑ xs) = length-drop n xs
 
-- Drop commutes with map.
drop-map : ‚àÄ {f : A ‚Üí B} (n : ‚Ñï) xs ‚Üí drop n (map f xs) ‚â° map f (drop n xs)
drop-map zero xs = refl
drop-map (suc n) [] = refl
drop-map (suc n) (a ‚à∑ xs) = drop-map n xs
 
-- Dropping from an empty list does nothing.
drop-[] : ‚àÄ m ‚Üí drop {A = A} m [] ‚â° []
drop-[] zero = refl
drop-[] (suc m) = refl
 
take++drop‚â°id : ‚àÄ n (xs : List A) ‚Üí take n xs ++ drop n xs ‚â° xs
take++drop‚â°id zero    xs       = refl
take++drop‚â°id (suc n) []       = refl
take++drop‚â°id (suc n) (x ‚à∑ xs) = cong (x ‚à∑_) (take++drop‚â°id n xs)
 
drop-take-suc : (xs : List A) (i : Fin (length xs)) ‚Üí let m = to‚Ñï i in
           drop m (take (suc m) xs) ‚â° [ lookup xs i ]
drop-take-suc (x ‚à∑ xs) zero    = refl
drop-take-suc (x ‚à∑ xs) (suc i) = drop-take-suc xs i
 
drop-take-suc-tabulate : ‚àÄ {n} (f : Fin n ‚Üí A) (i : Fin n) ‚Üí let m = to‚Ñï i in
                  drop m (take (suc m) (tabulate f)) ‚â° [ f i ]
drop-take-suc-tabulate f i rewrite sym (to‚Ñï-cast (sym (length-tabulate f)) i) | sym (lookup-tabulate f i)
  = drop-take-suc (tabulate f) (cast _ i)
 
-- Dropping m elements and then n elements is same as dropping m+n elements
drop-drop : (m n : ‚Ñï) ‚Üí (xs : List A) ‚Üí drop n (drop m xs) ‚â° drop (m + n) xs
drop-drop zero n xs = refl
drop-drop (suc m) n [] = drop-[] n
drop-drop (suc m) n (x ‚à∑ xs) = drop-drop m n xs
 
drop-all : (n : ‚Ñï) (xs : List A) ‚Üí n ‚â• length xs ‚Üí drop n xs ‚â° []
drop-all n       []       _ = drop-[] n
drop-all (suc n) (x ‚à∑ xs) p = drop-all n xs (s‚â§s‚Åª¬π p)

                   lookup (replicate n x) (cast (sym (length-replicate n)) i) ‚â° x

                 map f (replicate n x) ‚â° replicate n (f x)

-- filter
 
module _ {P : Pred A p} (P? : Decidable P) where
 
  length-filter : ‚àÄ xs ‚Üí length (filter P? xs) ‚â§ length xs
  length-filter []       = z‚â§n
  length-filter (x ‚à∑ xs) with ih ‚Üê length-filter xs | does (P? x)
  ... | false = m‚â§n‚áím‚â§1+n ih
  ... | true  = s‚â§s ih
 
  filter-all : ‚àÄ {xs} ‚Üí All P xs ‚Üí filter P? xs ‚â° xs
  filter-all {[]}     []         = refl
  filter-all {x ‚à∑ xs} (px ‚à∑ pxs) with P? x
  ... | no          ¬¨px = contradiction px ¬¨px
  ... | true  because _ = cong (x ‚à∑_) (filter-all pxs)
 
  filter-notAll : ‚àÄ xs ‚Üí Any (‚àÅ P) xs ‚Üí length (filter P? xs) < length xs
  filter-notAll (x ‚à∑ xs) (here ¬¨px) with P? x
  ... | false because _ = s‚â§s (length-filter xs)
  ... | yes          px = contradiction px ¬¨px
  filter-notAll (x ‚à∑ xs) (there any) with ih ‚Üê filter-notAll xs any | does (P? x)
  ... | false = m‚â§n‚áím‚â§1+n ih
  ... | true  = s‚â§s ih
 
  filter-some : ‚àÄ {xs} ‚Üí Any P xs ‚Üí 0 < length (filter P? xs)
  filter-some {x ‚à∑ xs} (here px)   with P? x
  ... | true because _ = z<s
  ... | no         ¬¨px = contradiction px ¬¨px
  filter-some {x ‚à∑ xs} (there pxs) with does (P? x)
  ... | true  = m‚â§n‚áím‚â§1+n (filter-some pxs)
  ... | false = filter-some pxs
 
  filter-none : ‚àÄ {xs} ‚Üí All (‚àÅ P) xs ‚Üí filter P? xs ‚â° []
  filter-none {[]}     []           = refl
  filter-none {x ‚à∑ xs} (¬¨px ‚à∑ ¬¨pxs) with P? x
  ... | false because _ = filter-none ¬¨pxs
  ... | yes          px = contradiction px ¬¨px
 
  filter-complete : ‚àÄ {xs} ‚Üí length (filter P? xs) ‚â° length xs ‚Üí
                    filter P? xs ‚â° xs
  filter-complete {[]}     eq = refl
  filter-complete {x ‚à∑ xs} eq with does (P? x)
  ... | false = contradiction eq (<‚áí‚â¢ (s‚â§s (length-filter xs)))
  ... | true  = cong (x ‚à∑_) (filter-complete (suc-injective eq))
 
  filter-accept : ‚àÄ {x xs} ‚Üí P x ‚Üí filter P? (x ‚à∑ xs) ‚â° x ‚à∑ (filter P? xs)
  filter-accept {x} Px with P? x
  ... | true because _ = refl
  ... | no         ¬¨Px = contradiction Px ¬¨Px
 
  filter-reject : ‚àÄ {x xs} ‚Üí ¬¨ P x ‚Üí filter P? (x ‚à∑ xs) ‚â° filter P? xs
  filter-reject {x} ¬¨Px with P? x
  ... | yes          Px = contradiction Px ¬¨Px
  ... | false because _ = refl
 
  filter-idem : filter P? ‚àò filter P? ‚âó filter P?
  filter-idem []       = refl
  filter-idem (x ‚à∑ xs) with does (P? x) in eq
  ... | false            = filter-idem xs
  ... | true  rewrite eq = cong (x ‚à∑_) (filter-idem xs)
 
  filter-++ : ‚àÄ xs ys ‚Üí filter P? (xs ++ ys) ‚â° filter P? xs ++ filter P? ys
  filter-++ []       ys = refl
  filter-++ (x ‚à∑ xs) ys with ih ‚Üê filter-++ xs ys | does (P? x)
  ... | true  = cong (x ‚à∑_) ih
  ... | false = ih

-- derun and deduplicate
 
module _ {R : Rel A p} (R? : B.Decidable R) where
 
  length-derun : ‚àÄ xs ‚Üí length (derun R? xs) ‚â§ length xs
  length-derun [] = ‚â§-refl
  length-derun (x ‚à∑ []) = ‚â§-refl
  length-derun (x ‚à∑ y ‚à∑ xs) with ih ‚Üê length-derun (y ‚à∑ xs) | does (R? x y)
  ... | true  = m‚â§n‚áím‚â§1+n ih
  ... | false = s‚â§s ih
 
  length-deduplicate : ‚àÄ xs ‚Üí length (deduplicate R? xs) ‚â§ length xs
  length-deduplicate [] = z‚â§n
  length-deduplicate (x ‚à∑ xs) = ‚â§-begin
    1 + length (filter (¬¨? ‚àò R? x) r) ‚â§‚ü® s‚â§s (length-filter (¬¨? ‚àò R? x) r) ‚ü©
    1 + length r                      ‚â§‚ü® s‚â§s (length-deduplicate xs) ‚ü©
    1 + length xs                     ‚â§-‚àé
    where
    open ‚â§-Reasoning renaming (begin_ to ‚â§-begin_; _‚àé to _‚â§-‚àé)
    r = deduplicate R? xs
 
  derun-reject : ‚àÄ {x y} xs ‚Üí R x y ‚Üí derun R? (x ‚à∑ y ‚à∑ xs) ‚â° derun R? (y ‚à∑ xs)
  derun-reject {x} {y} xs Rxy with R? x y
  ... | yes _    = refl
  ... | no  ¬¨Rxy = contradiction Rxy ¬¨Rxy
 
  derun-accept : ‚àÄ {x y} xs ‚Üí ¬¨ R x y ‚Üí derun R? (x ‚à∑ y ‚à∑ xs) ‚â° x ‚à∑ derun R? (y ‚à∑ xs)
  derun-accept {x} {y} xs ¬¨Rxy with R? x y
  ... | yes Rxy = contradiction Rxy ¬¨Rxy
  ... | no  _   = refl

  partition-defn []       = refl
  partition-defn (x ‚à∑ xs) with ih ‚Üê partition-defn xs | does (P? x)

-- _ ≥++_
 
 ≥++-defn : ‚àÄ (xs : List A) {ys} ‚Üí xs  ≥++ ys ‚â° reverse xs ++ ys
 ≥++-defn [] = refl
 ≥++-defn (x ‚à∑ xs) {ys} = begin
  (x ‚à∑ xs)              ≥++ ys   ‚â°‚ü®‚ü©
  xs          ≥++   x     ‚à∑ ys   ‚â°‚ü®‚ü©
  xs          ≥++ [ x ]  ++ ys   ‚â°‚ü®  ≥++-defn xs  ‚ü©
  reverse xs  ++ [ x ]  ++ ys   ‚â°‚ü® sym (++-assoc (reverse xs) _ _) ‚ü©
  (reverse xs ++ [ x ]) ++ ys   ‚â°‚ü® cong (_++ ys) (sym ( ≥++-defn xs)) ‚ü©
  (xs  ≥++ [ x ])        ++ ys   ‚â°‚ü®‚ü©
  reverse (x ‚à∑ xs)      ++ ys   ‚àé
 
-- Reverse-append of append is reverse-append after reverse-append.
 
++- ≥++ : ‚àÄ (xs {ys zs} : List A) ‚Üí (xs ++ ys)  ≥++ zs ‚â° ys  ≥++ xs  ≥++ zs
++- ≥++ [] = refl
++- ≥++ (x ‚à∑ xs) {ys} {zs} = begin
  (x ‚à∑ xs ++ ys)  ≥++ zs   ‚â°‚ü®‚ü©
  (xs ++ ys)  ≥++ x ‚à∑ zs   ‚â°‚ü® ++- ≥++ xs ‚ü©
  ys  ≥++ xs  ≥++ x ‚à∑ zs    ‚â°‚ü®‚ü©
  ys  ≥++ (x ‚à∑ xs)  ≥++ zs  ‚àé
 
-- Reverse-append of reverse-append is commuted reverse-append after append.
 
 ≥++- ≥++ : ‚àÄ (xs {ys zs} : List A) ‚Üí (xs  ≥++ ys)  ≥++ zs ‚â° ys  ≥++ xs ++ zs
 ≥++- ≥++ [] = refl
 ≥++- ≥++ (x ‚à∑ xs) {ys} {zs} = begin
  ((x ‚à∑ xs)  ≥++ ys)  ≥++ zs   ‚â°‚ü®‚ü©
  (xs  ≥++ x ‚à∑ ys)  ≥++ zs     ‚â°‚ü®  ≥++- ≥++ xs ‚ü©
  (x ‚à∑ ys)  ≥++ xs ++ zs      ‚â°‚ü®‚ü©
  ys  ≥++ (x ‚à∑ xs) ++ zs      ‚àé
 
-- Length of reverse-append
 
length- ≥++ : ‚àÄ (xs {ys} : List A) ‚Üí
             length (xs  ≥++ ys) ‚â° length xs + length ys
length- ≥++ [] = refl
length- ≥++ (x ‚à∑ xs) {ys} = begin
  length ((x ‚à∑ xs)  ≥++ ys)      ‚â°‚ü®‚ü©
  length (xs  ≥++ x ‚à∑ ys)        ‚â°‚ü® length- ≥++ xs ‚ü©
  length xs + length (x ‚à∑ ys)   ‚â°‚ü® +-suc _ _ ‚ü©
  length (x ‚à∑ xs) + length ys   ‚àé
 
-- map distributes over reverse-append.
 
map- ≥++ : (f : A ‚Üí B) (xs {ys} : List A) ‚Üí
          map f (xs  ≥++ ys) ‚â° map f xs  ≥++ map f ys
map- ≥++ f []            = refl
map- ≥++ f (x ‚à∑ xs) {ys} = begin
  map f ((x ‚à∑ xs)  ≥++ ys)         ‚â°‚ü®‚ü©
  map f (xs  ≥++ x ‚à∑ ys)           ‚â°‚ü® map- ≥++ f xs ‚ü©
  map f xs  ≥++ map f (x ‚à∑ ys)     ‚â°‚ü®‚ü©
  map f xs  ≥++ f x ‚à∑ map f ys     ‚â°‚ü®‚ü©
  (f x ‚à∑ map f xs)  ≥++ map f ys   ‚â°‚ü®‚ü©
  map f (x ‚à∑ xs)    ≥++ map f ys   ‚àé
 
-- A foldr after a reverse is a foldl.
 
foldr- ≥++ : ‚àÄ (f : A ‚Üí B ‚Üí B) b xs {ys} ‚Üí
            foldr f b (xs  ≥++ ys) ‚â° foldl (flip f) (foldr f b ys) xs
foldr- ≥++ f b []       {_}  = refl
foldr- ≥++ f b (x ‚à∑ xs) {ys} = begin
  foldr f b ((x ‚à∑ xs)  ≥++ ys)              ‚â°‚ü®‚ü©
  foldr f b (xs  ≥++ x ‚à∑ ys)                ‚â°‚ü® foldr- ≥++ f b xs ‚ü©
  foldl (flip f) (foldr f b (x ‚à∑ ys)) xs   ‚â°‚ü®‚ü©
  foldl (flip f) (f x (foldr f b ys)) xs   ‚â°‚ü®‚ü©
  foldl (flip f) (foldr f b ys) (x ‚à∑ xs)   ‚àé
 
-- A foldl after a reverse is a foldr.
 
foldl- ≥++ : ‚àÄ (f : B ‚Üí A ‚Üí B) b xs {ys} ‚Üí
            foldl f b (xs  ≥++ ys) ‚â° foldl f (foldr (flip f) b xs) ys
foldl- ≥++ f b []       {_}  = refl
foldl- ≥++ f b (x ‚à∑ xs) {ys} = begin
  foldl f b ((x ‚à∑ xs)  ≥++ ys)              ‚â°‚ü®‚ü©
  foldl f b (xs  ≥++ x ‚à∑ ys)                ‚â°‚ü® foldl- ≥++ f b xs ‚ü©
  foldl f (foldr (flip f) b xs) (x ‚à∑ ys)   ‚â°‚ü®‚ü©
  foldl f (f (foldr (flip f) b xs) x) ys   ‚â°‚ü®‚ü©
  foldl f (foldr (flip f) b (x ‚à∑ xs)) ys   ‚àé

-- reverse
 
-- reverse of cons is snoc of reverse.
 
unfold-reverse : ‚àÄ (x : A) xs ‚Üí reverse (x ‚à∑ xs) ‚â° reverse xs ‚à∑ ≥ x
unfold-reverse x xs =  ≥++-defn xs
 
-- reverse is an anti-homomorphism with respect to append.
 
reverse-++ : (xs ys : List A) ‚Üí
                     reverse (xs ++ ys) ‚â° reverse ys ++ reverse xs
reverse-++ xs ys = begin
  reverse (xs ++ ys)         ‚â°‚ü®‚ü©
  (xs ++ ys)  ≥++ []          ‚â°‚ü® ++- ≥++ xs ‚ü©
  ys  ≥++ xs  ≥++ []           ‚â°‚ü®‚ü©
  ys  ≥++ reverse xs          ‚â°‚ü®  ≥++-defn ys ‚ü©
  reverse ys ++ reverse xs   ‚àé
 
-- reverse is self-inverse.
 
reverse-selfInverse : SelfInverse {A = List A} _‚â°_ reverse
reverse-selfInverse {x = xs} {y = ys} xs‚Åª¬π‚âàys = begin
  reverse ys         ‚â°‚ü®‚ü©
  ys  ≥++ []          ‚â°‚ü® cong (_ ≥++ []) xs‚Åª¬π‚âàys ‚ü®
  reverse xs  ≥++ []  ‚â°‚ü®‚ü©
  (xs  ≥++ [])  ≥++ [] ‚â°‚ü®  ≥++- ≥++ xs ‚ü©
  []  ≥++ xs ++ []    ‚â°‚ü®‚ü©
  xs ++ []           ‚â°‚ü® ++-identity ≥ xs ‚ü©
  xs                 ‚àé
 
-- reverse is involutive.
 
reverse-involutive : Involutive {A = List A} _‚â°_ reverse
reverse-involutive = selfInverse‚áíinvolutive reverse-selfInverse
 
-- reverse is injective.
 
reverse-injective : Injective {A = List A} _‚â°_ _‚â°_ reverse
reverse-injective = selfInverse‚áíinjective reverse-selfInverse
 
-- reverse preserves length.
 
length-reverse : ‚àÄ (xs : List A) ‚Üí length (reverse xs) ‚â° length xs
length-reverse xs = begin
  length (reverse xs)   ‚â°‚ü®‚ü©
  length (xs  ≥++ [])    ‚â°‚ü® length- ≥++ xs ‚ü©
  length xs + 0         ‚â°‚ü® +-identity ≥ _ ‚ü©
  length xs             ‚àé
 
reverse-map : (f : A ‚Üí B) ‚Üí map f ‚àò reverse ‚âó reverse ‚àò map f
reverse-map f xs = begin
  map f (reverse xs) ‚â°‚ü®‚ü©
  map f (xs  ≥++ [])  ‚â°‚ü® map- ≥++ f xs ‚ü©
  map f xs  ≥++ []    ‚â°‚ü®‚ü©
  reverse (map f xs) ‚àé
 
reverse-foldr : ‚àÄ (f : A ‚Üí B ‚Üí B) b ‚Üí
                foldr f b ‚àò reverse ‚âó foldl (flip f) b
reverse-foldr f b xs = foldr- ≥++ f b xs
 
reverse-foldl : ‚àÄ (f : B ‚Üí A ‚Üí B) b xs ‚Üí
                foldl f b (reverse xs) ‚â° foldr (flip f) b xs
reverse-foldl f b xs = foldl- ≥++ f b xs

-- reverse, applyUpTo, and applyDownFrom
 
reverse-applyUpTo : ‚àÄ (f : ‚Ñï ‚Üí A) n ‚Üí reverse (applyUpTo f n) ‚â° applyDownFrom f n
reverse-applyUpTo f zero = refl
reverse-applyUpTo f (suc n) = begin
  reverse (f 0 ‚à∑ applyUpTo (f ‚àò suc) n)  ‚â°‚ü® reverse-++ [ f 0 ] (applyUpTo (f ‚àò suc) n) ‚ü©
  reverse (applyUpTo (f ‚àò suc) n) ‚à∑ ≥ f 0 ‚â°‚ü® cong (_‚à∑ ≥ f 0) (reverse-applyUpTo (f ‚àò suc) n) ‚ü©
  applyDownFrom (f ‚àò suc) n ‚à∑ ≥ f 0       ‚â°‚ü® applyDownFrom-‚à∑ ≥ f n ‚ü©
  applyDownFrom f (suc n)                ‚àé
 
reverse-upTo : ‚àÄ n ‚Üí reverse (upTo n) ‚â° downFrom n

reverse-applyDownFrom : ‚àÄ (f : ‚Ñï ‚Üí A) n ‚Üí reverse (applyDownFrom f n) ‚â° applyUpTo f n

  reverse (f n ‚à∑ applyDownFrom f n)  ‚â°‚ü® reverse-++ [ f n ] (applyDownFrom f n) ‚ü©
  reverse (applyDownFrom f n) ‚à∑ ≥ f n ‚â°‚ü® cong (_‚à∑ ≥ f n) (reverse-applyDownFrom f n) ‚ü©
  applyUpTo f n ‚à∑ ≥ f n               ‚â°‚ü® applyUpTo-‚à∑ ≥ f n ‚ü©
  applyUpTo f (suc n)                ‚àé
 
reverse-downFrom : ‚àÄ n ‚Üí reverse (downFrom n) ‚â° upTo n
reverse-downFrom = reverse-applyDownFrom id

-- _‚à∑ ≥_
 
‚à∑ ≥-injective : ‚àÄ xs ys ‚Üí xs ‚à∑ ≥ x ‚â° ys ‚à∑ ≥ y ‚Üí xs ‚â° ys √ó x ‚â° y
‚à∑ ≥-injective []          []          refl = refl , refl
‚à∑ ≥-injective (x ‚à∑ xs)    (y  ‚à∑ ys)   eq   with refl , eq‚Ä≤  ‚Üê ‚à∑-injective eq
